# Udacity_FEND_P1

For this project, I was given a plain mockup article in PDF format that held content. I was advised to recreate the mockup article using HTML elements. With doing so, I utilized Mozilla Developer Network for extended research to discover what HTML syntaxes to use.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
